SQL_STMT_U.val:
SELECT i.KundenNr, i.VkPreis, i.Rabatt, isnull(k.Matchcode,'') from INDIVIDUALPREIS i WITH(NOLOCK) left outer join kunden k WITH(NOLOCK) on k.ebene1=i.ebene1 and k.ebene2=i.ebene2 and k.ebene3=i.ebene3 and k.ebene4=i.ebene4 and k.KDNR=i.KundenNr WHERE i.Ebene1=:1 and i.Ebene2=:2 and i.Ebene3=:3 and i.Ebene4=:4 and ArtikelNr=':5'
union
SELECT i.KundenNr, i.VkPreis, i.Rabatt, isnull(k.Matchcode,'') from INDIVIDUALPREIS i WITH(NOLOCK) left outer join kunden k WITH(NOLOCK) on k.ebene1=i.ebene1 and k.ebene2=i.ebene2 and k.ebene3=i.ebene3 and k.ebene4=i.ebene4 and k.KDNR=i.KundenNr WHERE i.Ebene1=:6 and i.Ebene2=:7 and i.Ebene3=:8 and i.Ebene4=:9 and ArtikelNr=':5'
